hat\" .... oi o J ,,, ,,, ,,,, ,,,. J ,.,. ,,, ଧ ஷ::· .. li ଩ପ ஸ!4T Ji Jli ନǋ 1வi \u0011 Jஶi On the authority of Abu Amr- and it also said Abu Amrah--- Sufyaan ibn Abdullah (may Allah be pleased with him) who said: I said, \"0 Messenger of Allah, tell me a statement about Islam such that I will not have to ask anyone other than you.\" He answered, \"Say, 'I believe in Allah,' and then stand firm and steadfast to that.\" (Recorded by Muslim.) 'iL - \"a statement, words\" JLI - \"I ask\" \" , .Y' J • [Sufyaan then said,] \"O Messenger of Allah, what is the thing that you fear most for me?\" He [the Prophet (peace be upon him)] took hold of his own tongue and said, \"This.\" (The meaning of Abdullah ibn Sufyaan's narration is virtually the same.) General Comments About This Hadith This hadith is another instance in which a few words of the Prophet (peace be upon him) have expressed the entirety of Islam: Imaan and istiqaamah. Islam is based on tauheed and obedience to Allah. Tauheed is captured in the belief in Allah and obedience is captured in istiqaamah.</p>",
  "content_id": "<p>Kelanjutan Daftar Isi Jilid 2. Hadis #41 (lanjutan): komentar umum, tentang perawi (Abdullah ibn Amr ibn al-Ash), 'kami meriwayatkannya dalam kitab al-Hujjah...', dan ringkasan.</p><p>Hadis #42 ('Wahai anak Adam, selama engkau berdoa kepada-Ku...'): kosakata pilihan, takhrij, komentar umum, tentang perawi (Anas ibn Malik), pembahasan hadis qudsi: 'Allah Yang Maha Berkah dan Maha Tinggi berfirman', 'wahai anak Adam', 'selama engkau berdoa kepada-Ku', 'dan berharap kepada-Ku', 'Aku ampuni dosa-dosamu tanpa peduli', 'seandainya dosa-dosamu mencapai awan', 'kemudian engkau memohon ampun kepada-Ku, niscaya Aku ampuni engkau', 'seandainya engkau datang kepada-Ku dengan... dan engkau bertemu dengan-Ku tanpa menyekutukan-Ku dengan sesuatu pun...', poin-poin terkait, dan ringkasan.</p><p>Bagian akhir Daftar Isi Jilid 2 juga mencantumkan: Penutup (Epilog), Data Biografis, Glosarium, Daftar Pustaka (rujukan bahasa Inggris dan bahasa Arab), Daftar Gambar, Ayat-Ayat Al-Quran yang Dikutip, dan Indeks Umum. Kemudian disajikan teks Hadis #21 beserta komentar umum yang menekankan bahwa hadis ini merangkum seluruh Islam dalam dua kata: iman dan istiqamah — Islam dibangun di atas tauhid dan ketaatan kepada Allah.</p>",
